        <p class="about-text">I am currently seeking employment for a remote position where I can contribute, learn and grow.</p>
        <p class='about-text'>I gained my tech skills through a lot of self-study and through the <a href="http://www.makersacademy.com/" target='_blank'>Makers Academy</a> remote online bootcamp.  Their curriculum is project-based with an emphasis on test-driven development, object-oriented programming, pair programming and agile practices</p>
        <p class="about-text">I gained valuable experience working remotely with a cohort of people from 10 different countries using Github, Slack, Zoom and other remote technologies.</p>
        <br>
        <br>
        <p class='link'><%= link_to 'Read more...', about_index_path %></p>
        <br>
        <br>
        <br>
        <p class="about-text">Check out my Resume and CV!</p>
        <div class="col-md-6">
